{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01EjjDJ44CmJcLRBo8NXT1Z2","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Verification Proof: Story 0.1 — Sprint Execution Skill\n     2→\n     3→**Verifier:** Claude Opus 4.6 (black-box)\n     4→**Date:** 2026-03-16\n     5→**Container:** codeharness-verify\n     6→**CLI Version:** codeharness 0.14.0\n     7→\n     8→---\n     9→\n    10→## AC 1: Sprint-status.yaml parsing — finds current epic and next backlog story\n    11→\n    12→**Verified: PASS (partial — parsing logic confirmed, skill invocation blocked)**\n    13→\n    14→The `codeharness run` command reads sprint-status.yaml, parses `development_status`, and correctly identifies story counts by status.\n    15→\n    16→**Test 1: All backlog stories**\n    17→\n    18→```bash\n    19→docker exec -w /workspace codeharness-verify bash -c 'cat > _bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/sprint-status.yaml << \"SEOF\"\n    20→sprint: 1\n    21→development_status:\n    22→  epic-0: backlog\n    23→  0-1-sprint-execution-skill: backlog\n    24→  0-2-another-story: backlog\n    25→  epic-0-retrospective: optional\n    26→SEOF'\n    27→docker exec -w /workspace codeharness-verify codeharness run --json 2>&1 | head -1\n    28→```\n    29→\n    30→```output\n    31→{\"status\":\"info\",\"message\":\"Starting autonomous execution — 2 ready, 0 in progress, 0 verified, 0/2 done\"}\n    32→```\n    33→\n    34→**Test 2: Mixed statuses — done, in-progress, backlog across two epics**\n    35→\n    36→```bash\n    37→docker exec -w /workspace codeharness-verify bash -c 'cat > _bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/sprint-status.yaml << \"SEOF\"\n    38→sprint: 1\n    39→development_status:\n    40→  epic-0: done"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01354VA1GpspSScsnH2wHagv","session_id":"f9b706e3-1764-4868-a4a5-c90b37d26d0d","uuid":"d6fedac8-dac2-4b6c-b839-dbc088d6ce75","timestamp":"2026-03-27T12:25:28.763Z"}
